snippet.textDisplay:
Honestly, does Coke Studio require Autotune/Voice filter to produce an episode?
Compare this with many such episodes where pure magic was created just original by voice of a singer (e.g, Rahat Fate Ali khan ji).

And , there is nothing of Bharatiya in this episode. I am pretty sure Diljit can do much better than this.
An open invitation to run a 30 minutes show with his voice without any auto-tune.

Kumar Shanu sir will smile .

Humble request to CS : Please do not downgrade your standard to accomodate any singer who is popular. Popularity is not a benchmark of quality singing and we comeback to CS for quality production only.
